'''热带风暴阿利森'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Allison}}）是2001年大西洋飓风季期间于6月对[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]东南部构成灾难性打击的一场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]。作为飓风季的首场[[风暴|风暴]]，阿利森的持续时间在6月风暴中异常之长，保持热带或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]状态达15天之久。系统于2001年6月4日由[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]北部的一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glo">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}发展形成，之后不久就袭击了德克萨斯州北部海岸。气旋向北飘移穿越该州后转向南下，再度进入墨西哥湾。风暴继续向东北偏北方向移动，登陆[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]后穿越[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]和[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]。阿利森是继1998年的[[1998年热带风暴弗朗西丝|热带风暴弗朗西丝]]以来第一个吹袭德克萨斯州北部海岸线的风暴<ref name="ivey">{{cite web | author = John P. Ivey | year = 2002 | title = Flood Safety and Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.floodsafety.com/media/pdfs/texas/ivey.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130616063832/http://floodsafety.com/media/pdfs/texas/ivey.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-06-16 }}</ref>。

风暴沿途普降暴雨，德克萨斯州的最高降雨量超过1000毫米。[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]爆发了最严重的洪灾，成为受阿利森打击最沉重的地区。洪水淹没了超过7万套房屋，还摧毁了2744套民宅，导致3万人无家可归。休斯敦市区也被洪水淹没，对多家医院和商户构成严重破坏，全州共有23人死亡。阿利森沿途一共造成41人丧生，经济损失高达55亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5500000000|2001}}}}美元）。除德克萨斯州以外，受灾最严重的地区分别是路易斯安那州和[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]东南部。

风暴过去后，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣布阿利森沿途的75个县成为灾区，以便灾民申请援助。由于风暴造成的灾难性破坏和大量人员伤亡，其名称“阿利森”因此退役，今后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时使用。截至[[2013年大西洋飓风季|2013年]]，这仍然是唯一一场未达飓风强度但却导致名称退役的大西洋风暴。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Allison 2001 track.png}}
2001年5月21日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|非洲]]海岸并向西穿越[[大西洋|大西洋]]，这一过程中发展出的[[对流|对流]]很少。经过[[南美洲|南美洲]]和[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西南部以后，东风波于6月1日进入东北[[太平洋|太平洋]]。6月2日，系统在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]][[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）东南偏南方向约370公里海域发展出下层环流。东风波因南向气流影响被迫北上，于6月3日进入陆地上空。之前发展出的下层环流已经消散，但还是有中层环流存在。6月4日，系统进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]，其东面已经发展出深层对流。<ref name="TCR">{{cite web | author = Stacy R. Stewart | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131109010754/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2001allison.html | title = Tropical Storm Allison Tropical Cyclone Report | date = 2002-02-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2008-08-16 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2001allison.html | archivedate = 2013-11-09}}</ref>6月5日清晨，卫星图像显示墨西哥湾西北部有一股[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]形成，之后的报告进一步显示系统东部表面上方约数百英尺位置的阵风时速已经达到95公里<ref>{{cite report | author = Stewart | title = June 5 Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2001-06-05 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。

[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月5日中午12点，这股扰动天气发展出一片广阔的下层环流，并因此成为2001年大西洋飓风季的首场风暴，获名“阿利森”（{{lang|en|Allison}}）。气象部门预计气旋会有一定程度强化，但增强过程也会因[[海面温度|海面温度]]低而受阻<ref>{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Allison Discussion Number 1 | date = 2001-06-05 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.001.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618180118/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.001.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-06-18}}</ref>。由于中心仍属[[冷心低压|冷心]]，因此风暴起初还表现出[[亚热带气旋|亚热带天气系统特征]]。虽然有这样的不利因素影响，阿利森还是迅速增强至[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时95公里的最高强度，中心以东370公里外的风速仍然达到热带风暴强度，中心最低气压为1000[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.53[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref name="TCR" />。风暴起初的移动速度非常缓慢，并且因深层对流内有多个小漩涡的存在导致其中心位置很难确定<ref name="disc2">{{cite web | author = Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Allison Discussion Number 2 | date = 2001-06-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.002.html | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618175149/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.002.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2013-06-18}}</ref>。当天晚些时候，[[气象学|气象学家]]对气旋接下来的行进路线出现了几种不同的预测。其中一种认为阿利森会向西进入墨西哥；另一种认为气旋会向东逼近路易斯安那州南部。这个时候系统中心附近的风力较弱，降水也很少，大部分风雨都位于东面和北面<ref>{{cite web | author = Lawrence | title = Tropical Storm Allison Discussion Number 3 | date = 2001-06-05 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.003.html | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618175703/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/dis/al012001.discus.003.html}}</ref>。由于一个从东向西跨越[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]的副热带高压脊产生的转向气流影响<ref name="disc2" />，阿利森在接近[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]海岸线的过程中减弱，以风力时速80公里强度吹袭该州[[布拉佐里亚县|布拉佐里亚县]]的[[弗里波特_(德克萨斯州)|弗里波特]]（{{lang|en|Freeport}}）<ref name="TCR" />。风暴在陆地上迅速减弱，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于6月6日清晨开始停止发布有关气旋的公告<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | title = Tropical Depression Allison Public Advisory Number 4 | date = 2001-06-06 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618175625/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/pub/al012001.public.004.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/pub/al012001.public.004.html | archivedate = 2013-06-18}}</ref>。风暴降级成热带低气压后不久，地面观测发现深层对流附近有拉长的环流和模糊的中心重新形成<ref>{{cite web | author = Pasch | title = Tropical Depression Allison Discussion Number 4 | date = 2001-06-06 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001131059/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/ALLISON.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/ALLISON.html | archivedate = 2013-10-01}}</ref>。
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Allison-_Eye.jpg|left]]上空的亚热带风暴阿利森，可以看到其中存在一个[[风眼|眼状特征]]]]

低气压向北飘移至德克萨斯州的[[拉夫金_(德克萨斯州)|拉夫金]]，然后因北面的[[高气压|高气压]]系统影响导致基本停止前进<ref name="TCR" />。在德克萨斯州上空停止移动期间，气旋产生了倾盆大雨，降雨量最高的[[杰佛逊县_(德克萨斯州)|杰佛逊县]]西北部超过1033毫米<ref name="wpc">{{cite web | author = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall totals from Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921153603/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/allison2001.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/allison2001.html}}</ref>。6月7日，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]近海的副热带高压脊有所减弱，同时德克萨斯州西部的高压脊得到增强。这种变化促使热带低气压阿利森以顺时针方向环路移动，风暴开始向西南方向飘移。随着系统中心到达德克萨斯州[[沃克縣_(德克薩斯州)|沃克县]][[亨茨维尔_(德克萨斯州)|亨茨维尔]]（{{lang|en|Huntsville}}）上空，一片厚实的[[雨带|雨带]]开始在其后方形成，雨带范围从[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]向西延伸到德克萨斯州[[利柏提县_(德克萨斯州)|利柏提县]]，又引发了更多的洪灾<ref name="synoptic">{{cite web | author = Houston/Galveston National Weather Service (Synoptic Situation) | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Allison Floods, June 5–9, 2001 | accessdate = 2009-05-14 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/synoptic.htm | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090514182951/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/synoptic.htm | archivedate = 2009-05-14}}</ref>。阿利森这时的最低中心气压约为1004毫巴，最大持续风速只有每小时16公里<ref>{{cite web | author = Pereira | title = Storm Summary Number 12 for the Remnants of Allison | date = 2001-06-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812122426/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=12&dt=2001060809&status=remnants | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=12&dt=2001060809&status=remnants | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。6月9日晚到6月10日清晨，阿利森的残留再次到达墨西哥湾开放水域上空<ref>{{cite web | author = Pereira | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 19 | date = 2001-06-10 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=19&dt=2001061003&status=remnants | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812122752/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=19&dt=2001061003&status=remnants}}</ref>。低气压在德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]以南约100公里洋面再度进入几乎停止移动的状态，这时虽然外界环境中存在有利热带气旋发展的上层风，但系统没有表现出任何重新发展的迹象<ref>{{cite report | author = Stewart | title = June 10 Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2001-06-10 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。由于空气干燥，还有着中等强度西向[[风切变|风切变]]的双重不利影响，风暴转变成了亚热带气旋。亚热带低气压向东移动，其东面重新发展出新的下层环流，系统很快于6月11日登陆路易斯安那州[[摩根城_(路易斯安那州)|摩根城]]<ref name="TCR" />。与此同时，表面中心在其原本位置的[[罗盘方位|东北偏东]]方向重新形成，与中层环流对齐<ref>{{cite web | author = Clark | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 23 | date = 2001-06-11 | deadurl = no | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812125527/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=23&dt=2001061103&s | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=23&dt=2001061103&status=remnants}}</ref>。环流上空重新发展出强烈的[[雷暴|雷暴]]，阿利森在路易斯安那州东南部上空增强成亚热带风暴<ref name="TCR" />。风暴在[[密西西比州|密西西比州]][[格林縣_(密西西比州)|格林县]][[麦克莱恩_(密西西比州)|麦克莱恩]]（{{lang|en|McLain}}）附近进一步增强至持续风力时速70公里，最低气压约1000毫巴强度，其中还出现了一个非常清晰的[[风眼|眼状特征]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Roth & Mcelroy | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 25 | date = 2001-06-11 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=25&dt=2001061115&status=remnants | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812130326/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=25&dt=2001061115&status=remnants}}</ref>。
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Allison-_Carolina.gif|right]]上空的亚热带低气压阿利森]]

{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}6月12日凌晨0点，风暴正式降级成亚热带低气压。气旋的前进速度略有加快，向东北偏东方向先后途经密西西比州、[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]、[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]，到达[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[威尔明顿_(北卡罗来纳州)|威尔明顿]]附近时再度进入基本停止移动的状态<ref name="TCR" />。由于有一股[[冷锋|冷锋]]逐渐逼近，低气压经过北卡罗莱纳州，并且向东北方向加速行进了一段时间<ref>{{cite report | author = Avila | title = June 14 Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2001-06-14 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。虽然卫星和雷达图像都显示系统层次分明，但其移动速度仍然有所降低，并且以不规则的路线移动了一段时间<ref>{{cite report | author = Beven | title = June 14 Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2001-06-14 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，从路径上看类似一个很小的逆时针环<ref>{{cite web | author = Ziegenfelder & Mcelroy | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 38 | date = 2001-06-14 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812131334/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=38&dt=2001061421&status=remnants | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=38&dt=2001061421&status=remnants}}</ref>。接下来风暴开始总体向东北方向移动，于6月16日从[[德玛瓦半岛|德玛瓦半岛]]南部经过<ref>{{cite web | author = Mcelroy | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 46 | date = 2001-06-16 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=46&dt=2001061621&status=remnants | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812131612/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=46&dt=2001061621&status=remnants}}</ref>。系统残留于6月17日进入大西洋上空，在到达[[大西洋城|大西洋城]]以东海域期间重新强化，其北面环流产生暴雨。低气压与一股[[锋_(气象)|锋面]]产生相互作用并开始与之合并，同时朝东北方向的前进速度提高到了每小时21公里<ref>{{cite web | author = Mcelroy | title = Storm Summary Number 49 for the Remnants of Allison | date = 2001-06-17 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=49&dt=2001061715&status=remnants | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812132047/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=49&dt=2001061715&status=remnants}}</ref>。阿利森的残留在[[斜压|斜压]]过程中重新增强成亚热带风暴，但只维持了很短的时间，然后在[[纽约|纽约]][[长岛_(纽约)|长岛]]以南洋面转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="TCR" />。到了6月17日晚，低气压已经到达[[罗得岛州|罗得岛州]]近海，给[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]带去大量降水<ref>{{cite web | author = Clark | title = Storm Summary Number 51 for the Remnants of Allison | date = 2001-06-17 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812132421/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=51&dt=2001061803&status=remnants | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=51&dt=2001061803&status=remnants}}</ref>。6月18日，系统残留被冷锋吸收，最终于6月20日经过[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[开普雷斯|开普雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）以南海域期间消散<ref name="TCR" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
风暴形成后不久，[[加尔维斯顿县|加尔维斯顿县]]政府向[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]最西面不受[[加尔维斯顿海塘|加尔维斯顿海塘]]保护的区域发布了自愿撤离令<ref name="TCR" />。该岛到[[波利瓦尔半岛_(德克萨斯州)|波利瓦尔半岛]]（{{lang|en|Bolivar Peninsula}}）之间的轮渡服务予以暂停，[[布拉佐里亚县|布拉佐里亚县]]的[[冲浪海滩_(德克萨斯州)|瑟夫赛德]]（{{lang|en|Surfside}}）也收到了自愿撤离令<ref name="nws1">{{cite web | author = Houston/Galveston National Weather Service | year = 2001 | title = Hurricane Local Statement (1) | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/HLSHOU.1.txt | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081108205317/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/HLSHOU.1.txt | archivedate = 2008-11-08}}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心针对阿利森发布首份公告时，德克萨斯州[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[萨金特_(德克萨斯州)|萨金特]]到路易斯安那州[[摩根城_(路易斯安那州)|摩根城]]之间地区收到了[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="disc1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 2001 | title = Tropical Storm Allison Discussion #1 | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/pub/al012001.public.001.html | archivedate = 2013-06-18 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130618175822/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2001/pub/al012001.public.001.html}}</ref>。风暴登陆后，德克萨斯州东部多个地区收到了山洪爆发预警和警告<ref name="nws3">{{cite web | author = Houston/Galveston National Weather Service | year = 2001 | title = Hurricane Local Statement (3) | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/HLSHOU.5.txt | archivedate = 2008-11-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081108205402/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/HLSHOU.5.txt | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻休斯敦办事处在多场洪灾爆发期间发布了99份山洪爆发警告，平均每份的提前时间约为40分钟；驻路易斯安那州[[莱克查尔斯_(路易斯安那州)|莱克查尔斯]]办事处则发布了47份山洪爆发警告，平均每份的提前时间为24分钟；驻[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]和[[巴吞鲁日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞鲁日]]办事处也发布了87份山洪爆发警告，平均每份提前39分钟。所有这些警告中只有30次在发布后没有出现山洪爆发<ref name="nws">{{cite web | author = United States Department of Commerce | year = 2001 | title = Tropical Storm Allison Heavy Rains and Floods in Texas and Louisiana | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nws.noaa.gov/om/assessments/pdfs/allison.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140717060316/http://www.nws.noaa.gov/om/assessments/pdfs/allison.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-17}}</ref>。

[[塔拉赫西|塔拉赫西]]在阿利森向北逼近的前一天开设了一个避难所，有7位工作人员安置了12人。另有两个避难所进入待命状态。佛罗里达州西北狭长地带的居民收到了洪水警报。<ref name="flalpre">{{cite web | author = United States Red Cross | year = 2001 | title = Tropical Storm Allison Florida Situation Report | accessdate = 2008-10-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081030025639/http://redcross.tallytown.com/situation/allison-01.pdf | archivedate = 2008-10-30 | url = http://redcross.tallytown.com/situation/allison-01.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>

