热带风暴阿利森途经德克萨斯州和中大西洋各州时引发了重大洪涝灾害。降雨量超过890毫米的[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]受灾最为严重。整场风暴一共夺走了41人的生命，其中27人溺毙，造成的破坏价值高达55亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5500000000|2001}}}}美元），成为美国历史上最致命、造成损失最惨重的热带风暴。<ref name="TCR" />

=== 德克萨斯州 ===
加尔维斯顿岛受到高达2.5米水墙的冲击，其上还有更高的波浪，导致海岸沿线出现越流。加尔维斯顿码头的风速达到每小时69公里。阿利森在德克萨斯州上空基本停止移动期间令该州普降暴雨<ref name="TCR" />。海滩受到了轻度[[侵蚀作用|侵蚀]]<ref name="hogaprelim">{{cite web | author = Houston/Galveston National Weather Service | year = 2001 | title = Preliminary Report (Houston/Galveston) | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | archivedate = 2008-11-08 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/SATPSHHOU.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081108203053/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/SATPSHHOU.txt}}</ref>。爆发的山洪持续了数天之久<ref name="synoptic" />，全州降雨量最高的杰佛逊县西北部超过了1033毫米，休斯敦港也有940毫米<ref name="wpc" />。休斯敦经历了持续时间不长的倾盆大雨，连续6天的降雨量共计达到980毫米<ref name="rms">{{cite web | author = Risk Management Solutions | year = 2001 | title = Tropical Storm Allison Event Report | accessdate = 2014-02-23 | url = http://www.rms.com/Publications/TS_Allison.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223011413/http://www.rms.com/Publications/TS_Allison.pdf | archivedate = 2014-02-23 }}</ref>。整个[[哈里斯县_(德克萨斯州)|哈里斯县]]有9.5万套移动房屋和7.3万套房屋被降水引发的洪水淹没<ref name="ivey" />。热带风暴阿利森摧毁了2744套民宅，导致3万人流离失所，单住房所受破坏就价值17.6亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1760000000|2001}}}}美元）<ref name="rms" />。
[[File:TS_Allison_Texas_flooding.jpg|right]]

世界上最大的医疗园区[[德克萨斯医疗中心|德克萨斯医疗中心]]有多间医院在星期五晚上受到风暴的突然袭击导致严重破坏。[[贝勒医学院|贝勒医学院]]受到价值4.95亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|495000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失。这所医学院失去了9万只用于研究的动物，6万套肿瘤样本，以及25年的科研数据。与其隔街相对的[[德克萨斯大学休斯敦健康科学中心|德克萨斯大学休斯敦健康科学中心]]失去了数以千计的实验动物。整个医疗中心一共遭受了超过20亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|2000000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失。<ref name="rms" />
[[File:Allison_Flood_Houston.jpg|thumb]]

连接休斯敦市中心大部分大型办公楼的[[休斯敦隧道系统|地下隧道系统]]被洪水淹没，同样被淹的还有临近[[水牛河|水牛河]]（{{lang|en|Buffalo Bayou}}）的许多街道和停车场。同样位于市中心的[[休斯敦剧院区|休斯敦剧院区]]同样损失惨重，休斯敦交响乐团、休斯敦大歌剧院和艾莱剧院损失了价值数百万美元的服装、[[乐器|乐器]]、乐谱、档案和其他物件。到6月9日午夜时分，全市几乎所有高速公路和主要道路都被数英尺深的水淹没，成百上千的司机被迫抛下汽车逃往高处。<ref name="rms" />

虽然整片整片的街区都被大规模洪水破坏，但被淹的民房中没有出现人员溺亡的情况。该地区的死亡人数中有12人当时正在开车、6人正在行走、3人触电身亡、1人身在电梯之中<ref name="ivey" />。此外，[[橙县_(德克薩斯州)|橙县]]的[[莫里斯维尔_(德克萨斯州)|莫里斯维尔]]（{{lang|en|Mauriceville}}）还有一名正在沟渠里游泳的男子淹死<ref name="nws" />。整个德克萨斯州一共遭受了52亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5200000000|2001}}}}美元）的巨额损失<ref name="texasdamage">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Texas | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~450007 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222031003/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~450007 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。

=== 路易斯安那州 ===
[[File:TS_Allison-LA.jpg|thumb]]查克贝的洪灾]]
首次登陆期间，阿利森的大规模环流给路易斯安那州西南部带去暴雨<ref name="nws2">{{cite web | author = Lake Charles National Weather Service | year = 2001 | title = Hurricane Local Statement (2) | accessdate = 2008-11-08 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/NEWPSHLCH.1.txt | archivedate = 2008-11-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081108203115/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/hgx/projects/allison01/textproducts/NEWPSHLCH.1.txt | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。数天后，气旋以亚热带风暴形式袭击该州，产生了更多的降水。降雨量最高的[[蒂博_(路易斯安那州)|蒂博]]达到758毫米，令阿利森成为继1989年的另一场[[1989年热带风暴阿利森|同名热带风暴]]以来给该州带去降水最多的热带气旋<ref name="summary">{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | year = 2001 | title = Remnants of ALLISON Advisory Number 52 | accessdate = 2014-08-12 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=52&dt=2001061909&status=remnants | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140813023333/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=ALLISON&adnum=52&dt=2001061909&status=remnants}}</ref>。路易斯安那州东南部大部分地区降雨量都在255毫米以上<ref name="wpc" />。风力则总体较小，持续风速最高的是莱克弗龙特（{{lang|en|Lakefront}}），为每小时61公里，阵风时速最高的是加登湾（{{lang|en|Bay Gardene}}），达到85公里。风暴在德克萨斯州产生降水期间还给[[卡梅伦_(路易斯安那州)|卡梅伦]]带去了0.75米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="glo" />。|group="注"}}<ref name="TCR" />。阿利森北上穿越德克萨斯州期间，其外围雨带在[[扎卡里_(路易斯安那州)|扎卡里]]附近催生出一场[[藤田级数|藤田级数]]达到{{lang|en|F1}}级的[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，破坏了多棵树木和一条输电线缆。受损的线缆击中了一辆卡车，车上一名男子丧生<ref name="latorn">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report For Louisiana | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432467 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030830/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432467 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。

阿利森首次登陆时产生的暴雨导致大量房屋和商户被淹。阵风令[[卡梅伦堂区_(路易斯安那州)|卡梅伦堂区]]的10套房屋屋顶受到轻度破坏，路易斯安那州82号高速公路部分路段被风暴潮淹没<ref name="ladam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Louisiana 2 | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432482 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030835/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432482 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。天气系统再次登陆后又产生了更多的降水，[[圣坦曼尼堂区_(路易斯安那州)|圣坦曼尼堂区]]有上千套房屋被淹<ref name="ladam2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report For Louisiana 3 | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432494 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030845/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432494 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，[[圣贝尔纳堂区_(路易斯安那州)|圣贝尔纳堂区]]也有80套<ref name="ladam3">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Louisiana 4 | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432495 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030850/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432495 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，该州其它地区还有数百套。洪水迫使[[东巴吞鲁日堂区_(路易斯安那州)|东巴吞鲁日堂区]]的约1800位居民离开家园<ref name="ladam4">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Louisiana 5 | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432484 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030841/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~432484 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。许多道路因洪水导致无法通行，地面径流还引起河流严重泛滥。[[卡温顿_(路易斯安那州)|卡温顿]]境内的博格法拉亚河（{{lang|en|Bogue Falaya River}}）两次接近历史最高水位<ref name="ladam2" />。阿米特河（{{lang|en|Amite River}}）与科米特河（{{lang|en|Comite River}}）都到达了继1983年以来的最高水位。此外，曼查克河沿线的防洪堤决堤，淹没了许多道路和房屋<ref name="ladam4" />。整个路易斯安那州一共遭受了6500万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|65000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="rms" />。

=== 美国东南部 ===
[[File:Allison_2001_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]一夜之间的降雨量就超过255毫米<ref name="msdam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Mississipp | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436002 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030905/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436002 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，该州西南部部分区域更超过380毫米<ref name="wpc" />。洪水令大量房屋受损，还淹没了许多道路<ref name="msdam" />。源于风暴的雷暴活动催生出4场龙卷风<ref name="TCR" />，其中袭击[[格尔夫波特_(密西西比州)|格尔夫波特]]的一场损及10套房屋<ref name="mstorn">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Mississippi (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436004 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030911/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436004 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。[[乔治县_(密西西比州)|乔治县]]有15套房屋因强烈雷暴受损，还有10套被毁，导致5人受伤<ref name="msthun">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Mississippi (3) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436012 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030916/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~436012 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。整个密西西比州遭受了超过100万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="msdam" /><ref name="mstorn" /><ref name="msthun" />。[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]的降雨量为中等水平，但[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]附近地区超过了255毫米<ref name="wpc" />。[[克伦肖县|克伦肖县]]有许多道路因暴雨被迫封闭<ref name="aldam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Alabama | accessdate = 2007-12-22 |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419596 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030755/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419596 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。风暴与高气压共同影响，令该州南部出现沿海洪灾<ref name="aldam2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Alabama (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419592 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030750/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419592 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。阿利森在[[莫比尔县|莫比尔县]]催生出一场{{lang|en|[[藤田级数|F0]]}}级龙卷风，导致有房屋的屋顶受到轻度破坏<ref name="altorn2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Alabama (3) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419588 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222020830/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~419588 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，另外还在[[卡温顿县_(阿拉巴马州)|卡温顿县]]催生了一场同样为{{lang|en|F0}}级的龙卷风，导致6户民房和一座教堂轻微受损<ref name="altorn2" />。

风暴与其北面存在的高气压系统之间产生了强烈的气压梯度，导致佛罗里达州海岸出现强烈[[离岸流|离岸流]]，[[艾斯康比亚县_(佛罗里达州)|艾斯康比亚县]]的[[彭萨科拉海滩|彭萨科拉海滩]]（{{lang|en|Pensacola Beach}}）为此启用了通常只用于风暴警告的警报器<ref name="flrip">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Florida | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423536 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030810/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423536 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。佛罗里达州海岸共有5人因离岸流丧生<ref name="flrip2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Florida (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423543 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030815/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423543 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。风暴的外围雨带给佛罗里达州西北狭长地带带去爆雨，一天内降雨量就超过了280毫米。[[塔拉哈西地区机场|塔拉哈西地区机场]]在24小时内的降雨量达到257毫米，刷新了1969年创下的纪录<ref name="fldam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Florida (3) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423575 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030820/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423575 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。整个佛罗里达州共有10户民房被毁，599套受损，其中196套程度严重，受损房屋主要分布在[[莱昂县_(佛罗里达州)|莱昂县]]<ref name="fladam">{{cite report | author = Gathana Parmenas | year = 2001 | title = Detailed Damage Assessment Summary in Florida}}</ref>。包括因离岸流造成的人员丧生在内，全州共有8人遇难<ref name="TCR" />，经济损失约2000万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|20000000|2001}}}}美元）<ref name="fldam" />。

乔治亚州出现暴雨，多个地点的24小时降雨量达到255毫米。洪水导致多条河流溢出，其中[[奥科尼河|奥科尼河]]（{{lang|en|Oconee River}}）位于[[鲍德温县_(乔治亚州)|鲍德温县]][[县城|县城]][[米利奇维尔|米利奇维尔]]（{{lang|en|Milledgeville}}）境内河段水位高达10.3米。该州西南部降雨量最大，许多桥梁和道路被冲毁，另外还有大量道路被淹。乔治亚州[[州长|州长]][[罗伊·巴恩斯|罗伊·巴恩斯]]（{{lang|en|Roy Barnes}}）宣传州内7个县进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="gadam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for Georgia | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~424563 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030825/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~424563 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。风暴还催生了两场龙卷风<ref name="TCR" />。阿利森的外围雨带在南卡罗莱纳州催生出10场龙卷风<ref name="TCR" />和多个漏斗云，不过大部分都只构成轻度破坏，有一所法院受损、多棵树木折断<ref name="sctorn">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for South Carolina | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446450 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030957/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446450 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，还有多条供电线路中断<ref name="sctorn2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for South Carolina (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446449 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030952/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446449 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。北卡罗莱纳州的降雨量在305到406毫米之间，[[马丁县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|马丁县]]几乎所有的道路都被迫封闭，还有25套民宅受损<ref name="ncdam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for North Carolina | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441768 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030942/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441768 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。[[哈利法克斯县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|哈利法克斯县]]东部还有一座桥梁被严重的洪水冲毁<ref name="ncdam2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Report for North Carolina (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441767 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030937/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441767 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，另有多辆汽车被淹<ref name="summary" />，全州因路面湿滑引发了9起交通事故<ref name="TCR" />。

=== 中大西洋各州和美国东北部 ===
[[File:TS_Allison-PA.JPG|right]]因洪水造成的破坏]]
[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]降下小雨，该州东南和西南部降雨量超过76毫米<ref name="wpc" />。地面因含水量饱和导致土层松软，一棵树因此倒塌，砸中一人导致伤重不治<ref name="usa">{{cite news | author = USA Today.com | title = Allison was weak, but a killer | accessdate = 2014-08-13 | archivedate = 2013-12-13 | date = 2001-07-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213020114/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2001/atlantic/allison-final-story.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2001/atlantic/allison-final-story.htm}}</ref>。阿利森还在该州催生了一场龙卷风<ref name="TCR" />。[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]出现中等程度降水，[[乔治城_(华盛顿哥伦比亚特区)|乔治城]]的降雨量有66毫米<ref name="dcrain">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Washington D.C.}}</ref>。[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]的[[登顿_(马里兰州)|登顿]]降雨量达到190毫米，导致11条道路封闭，还有41条受到冲蚀。该州东部海岸降雨量较少，只有25到50毫米。全州受到的破坏很小，并且没有出现人员丧生<ref name="maryall">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Maryland}}</ref>。[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]降雨量为中等，其中最高的[[格林伍德_(特拉华州)|格林伍德]]达到106毫米，不过没有出现因这场风暴造成破坏的报道<ref name="delall">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Delaware | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423153 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030800/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423153 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。

阿利森与逐渐逼近的冷锋共同作用，给整个宾夕法尼亚州东南部带去暴雨，[[巴克斯县|巴克斯县]][[查尔方特_(宾夕法尼亚州)|查尔方特]]（{{lang|en|Chalfont}}）的降雨量达到全州最高的258毫米，[[费城|费城]]部分地区也有超过76毫米。降水引起多条河流上涨，内沙米尼溪（{{lang|en|Neshaminy Creek}}）位于[[兰霍恩_(宾夕法尼亚州)|兰霍恩]]（{{lang|en|Langhorne}}）境内河段水位达到5.1米。该州东南部还有多条河流和溪流水位超过3米。降水还导致许多树木倒塌、输电线缆中断，导致风暴期间该州有7万人失去电力供应。洪水冲蚀了许多道路和桥梁，还包括[[宾夕法尼亚州东南地区交通局|宾夕法尼亚州东南地区交通局]]的部分铁路干线。此外还有241户民房被毁，另有1386套受损。一家[[道奇汽车|道奇汽车]]经销商有150辆车受到水淹。数百人因所在建筑被洪水破坏而需要救援。[[蒙哥马利县_(宾夕法尼亚州)|蒙哥马利县]]上莫兰德乡（{{lang|en|Upper Moreland Township}}）的乡村绿色综合公寓{{lang|en|A}}幢地下堂有一台干洗机因洪水导致脱落，砸破了一条天然气管线，进而因天然气泄露引起爆炸并引发火灾，夺走了6人的生命。由于建筑物周围完全被洪水包围，消防员无法提供援助。此外，还有一名男子因车落入河中而溺亡<ref name="penndam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Pennsylvania | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~445815 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030948/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~445815 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。整个宾夕法尼亚州一共遭受了2.15亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|215000000|2001}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="rms" />。

风暴给[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]带去暴雨，[[海洋县|海洋县]]的[[塔克顿_(新泽西州)|塔克顿]]降雨量达到全州最高的205毫米。降水还导致河流泛滥，[[梅特德空克河|梅特德空克河]]（{{lang|en|Metedeconk River}}）位于[[雷克伍德_(新泽西州)|雷克伍德]]（{{lang|en|Lakewood}}）境内的北部河段上涨到了2.5米。洪水导致许多道路封闭，其中包括多条州级公路<ref name="njdam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in New Jersey | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~440625 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030927/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~440625 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。[[大西洋城|大西洋城]]出现时速71公里的阵风，刮倒多棵树木，还令多条供电线路中断，导致超过1.3万人家中停电。许多人因水位太高需要救援，但该州没有出现人员丧生，总体破坏程度也很轻<ref name="njdam2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in New Jersey (2) | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~440624 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030922/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~440624 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。

热带风暴阿利森导致[[纽约州|纽约州]]山洪爆发，多个地区在一小时内降雨量就达75毫米，[[威斯特彻斯特县|威斯特彻斯特县]]的格兰提斯普林斯（{{lang|en|Granite Springs}}）达到全州最高的146毫米。降水导致河流泛滥，[[莫瓦河|莫瓦河]]（{{lang|en|Mahwah River}}）的浪头有1米高。降雨令24套房屋和多家商店受损，[[纽约|纽约]]地区还有多条重要公路因洪水封闭。该州没有因这场风暴导致人员丧生，总体所受破坏也很小<ref name="nydam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in New York | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441144 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030932/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~441144 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>。[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]的情况类似，[[温德姆县_(康涅狄格州)|温德姆县]][[庞弗里特_(康涅狄格州)|庞弗里特]]（{{lang|en|Pomfret}}）的降雨量达到全州最高的183毫米<ref name="condam2">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Connecticut | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423074 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222020834/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~423074 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>，导致多条道路封闭，还有多套房屋受到轻度损伤。扬蒂克河位于扬蒂克（{{lang|en|Yantic}}）境内河段上涨至3.4米<ref name="condam2" />，[[汉普顿_(康涅狄格州)|汉普顿]]（{{lang|en|Hampton}}）有一个私人水坝决堤，一条州级公路因此封闭<ref name="condam2" />。[[罗得岛州|罗得岛州]][[普罗维登斯县|普罗维登斯县]][[北史密斯菲尔德|北史密斯菲尔德]]（{{lang|en|North Smithfield}}）的降雨量达到180毫米，许多道路和房屋被洪水冲毁，[[福斯特_(罗德岛州)|福斯特]]（{{lang|en|Foster}}）还有一座木屋被毁<ref name="condam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Rhode Island | accessdate = 2012-03-03 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446298 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120303051203/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~446298 | archivedate = 2012-03-03}}</ref>。

阿利森外围雨带中一片与其它部分分离的雷暴在[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[乌斯特县_(马萨诸塞州)|乌斯特县]]和[[米德尔塞克斯县_(马萨诸塞州)|米德尔塞克斯县]]各催生出一场{{lang|en|[[藤田级数|F1]]}}级龙卷风，共有上百棵树木受到影响，还有一套房屋和一处小型露营地受到破坏。[[乌斯特县_(马萨诸塞州)|乌斯特县]]的[[莱明斯特_(马萨诸塞州)|莱明斯特]]（{{lang|en|Leominster}}）和米德尔塞克斯县的[[雪莉_(马萨诸塞州)|雪莉]]（{{lang|en|Shirley}}）有许多树木受到[[微下击暴流|微下击暴流]]的破坏。风暴产生的[[闪电|闪电]]击中了两套房屋，令其严重受损，但没有给其它地方构成较大影响。气旋还给该州带去中等强度降水，降雨量范围在75到125毫米之间，导致排水和交通受到影响。整个马萨诸塞州一共遭受了40万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|400000|2001}}}}美元）的损失。<ref name="madam">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2001 | title = Event Record Details for Tropical Storm Allison in Massachusetts | accessdate = 2007-12-22 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~433376 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071222030900/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~433376 | archivedate = 2007-12-22}}</ref>

== 善后 ==
风暴过后的几个星期里，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]共计宣布德克萨斯州<ref name="txdeclar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Texas Severe Storms & Flooding | accessdate = 2012-03-15 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6438 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134321/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6438}}</ref>、路易斯安那州南部<ref name="ladeclar">{{cite web | author = Fema | year = 2001 | title = Louisiana Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2012-01-05 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=116 | archivedate = 2012-01-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120105170316/http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=116}}</ref>、密西西比州南部<ref name="msdeclar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Mississippi Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2006-06-11 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=118 | archivedate = 2012-01-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120106055247/http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=118}}</ref>、佛罗里达州西北部<ref name="fldeclar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Florida Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2006-06-11 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=117 | archivedate = 2012-01-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120106053123/http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=117}}</ref>和宾夕法尼亚州东南部的75个县为灾区<ref name="padeclar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Pennsylvania Tropical Storm Allison | accessdate = 2006-06-11 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=119 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134325/http://www.fema.gov/news/event.fema?id=119 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。灾民因此可以获得包括临时住房、紧急上门维修和其它与灾害相关的费用援助。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]还会承担瓦砾清理、与救灾相关的应急服务以及修理或更换包括道路、桥梁在内各种公共设施费用的75%<ref name="txdeclar" />。
[[File:Allison-_Red_Cross.jpg|right]]

阿利森过去几周后，联邦紧急事务管理局在德克萨斯州东南部开设了6家灾难恢复中心，为申请灾害援助的灾民提供救灾相关信息<ref name="txdrc">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Disaster Recovery Centers To Open | accessdate = 2014-08-13 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6430 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134328/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6430 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]和[[救世军|救世军]]最多开设了48个避难所，为被迫离开家园的灾民提供了近30万顿膳食。[[国家灾难医疗系统|国家灾难医疗系统]]在休斯敦部署了一家配备有88名专业人士的临时医院，为近500人提供了救助<ref name="txhos">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Mobile Military Hospital Provides Emergency Care For Houston's Citizens | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6410 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134400/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6410}}</ref>。35个志愿组织为德克萨斯州灾民提供包括食品、衣物在内的多种援助，还有志愿者帮助修复房屋<ref name="txvol">{{cite web | author = FEMA | date = 2001-07-03 | title = Quiet Heroes — Voluntary Agencies | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140813092220/http://www.fema.gov/news-release/2001/07/03/quiet-heroes-voluntary-agencies | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-13 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news-release/2001/07/03/quiet-heroes-voluntary-agencies | archivedate = 2014-08-13}}</ref>。由于有近5万辆车被淹或被毁，许多人试图隐瞒车辆历史，将其卖到全国各地<ref name="txcar">{{cite web | author = FEMA | date = 2001-07-02 | title = Buyer Beware: Flood-Damaged Cars Being Sold | accessdate = 2014-08-13 | archivedate = 2014-08-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140813092304/http://www.fema.gov/news-release/2001/07/02/buyer-beware-flood-damaged-cars-being-sold | url = http://www.fema.gov/news-release/2001/07/02/buyer-beware-flood-damaged-cars-being-sold}}</ref>。极其严重的洪灾以后发生了[[蚊|蚊虫]]爆发，不过联邦紧急事务管理局提供援助控制了局势<ref name="txmosq">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = FEMA Funding Mosquito Control | accessdate = 2012-03-15 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6412 | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134416/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6412}}</ref>。风暴过去6个月后，一共有约12万德克萨斯州居民申请了10.5亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1050000000|2001}}}}美元）的联邦救灾援助<ref name="txaid">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Six Months After Allison, Disaster Assistance Reaches $1.05 Billion | accessdate = 2006-06-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120315134448/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6219 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-03-15 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6219}}</ref>。

路易斯安那州也像德克萨斯州一样出现了蚊虫爆发。当地只采用[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]和[[美国鱼类及野生动物管理局|美国鱼类及野生动物管理局]]认可的农药来控制虫害<ref name="lamos">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Responsible Response to Mosquitoes | accessdate = 2010-06-08 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6129 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608014323/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6129 | archivedate = 2010-06-08}}</ref>。联邦紧急事务管理局官员警告业主洪水的危险性包括霉菌和细菌等<ref name="lacl">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Drying Out, Cleaning Up After Allison | accessdate = 2010-06-08 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6128 | archivedate = 2010-06-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608014738/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6128}}</ref>。风暴过去3个月后，共有略超过10万名路易斯安那州居民申请了总额超过1.1亿美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|110000000|2001}}}}美元）的联邦援助。其中有2500万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|25000000|2001}}}}美元）属于商业贷款，此外还有800万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|8000000|2001}}}}美元）用于社区和州立机构的公共服务<ref name="laidsum">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Summary Of Louisiana Disaster Assistance | archivedate = 2010-06-08 | accessdate = 2006-06-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608043320/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6049 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6049}}</ref>。佛罗里达州有超过750位洪水灾民申请总额129万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1290000|2001}}}}美元）的政府援助<ref name="flaid">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = $1.2 Million Approved For Florida's Allison Flood Victims | accessdate = 2011-09-17 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6016 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110917064815/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=6016 | archivedate = 2011-09-17}}</ref>。宾夕法尼亚州共有1670名洪水灾民申请总额1150万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|11500000|2001}}}}美元）的联邦援助，其中340万美元（2001年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|3400000|2001}}}}美元）用于更换宾夕法尼亚州东南地区交通局位于[[蒙哥马利县_(宾夕法尼亚州)|蒙哥马利县]][[华盛顿堡_(宾夕法尼亚州)|华盛顿堡]]（{{lang|en|Fort Washington}}）境内的一座铁路桥梁<ref name="paid">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2001 | title = Disaster Aid, Loans for Pennsylvanians Near $11.5 Million | accessdate = 2010-06-08 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=5974 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608005429/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=5974 | archivedate = 2010-06-08}}</ref>。

=== 退役 ===
由于这场风暴造成了极其惨重的人员伤亡和经济损失，其名称“阿利森”因此退役，今后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时使用<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml#retired | title = Retired Hurricane Names Since 1954 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-03-16 | accessdate = 2014-07-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140709181817/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnames_history.shtml | archivedate = 2014-07-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。这仍然是唯一一场未达飓风强度但却导致名称退役的大西洋风暴，直至[[2015年大西洋飓风季|2015年]]风暴“[[熱帶風暴埃里卡|埃里卡]]”（{{lang|en|Erika}}）退役。用来替换的新名称是“安德烈亚”（{{lang|en|Andrea}}），于[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]期间[[2007年亚热带风暴安德烈亚|首度采用]]<ref>{{cite web | author = Jamie R. Rhome, Jack Beven, and Mark Willis | year = 2007 | title = Subtropical Storm Andrea Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-05-23 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL012007_Andrea.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2014-03-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330144217/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL012007_Andrea.pdf | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

